en.title: Congratulations Kenny Wong for Amazing Acievement!
en.content:
FE Congratulates new Presidential Director Kenny Wong, who is the 1st FE Member to achieved PD status in 30 days of joining FE! A special Outstanding Achievement Trophy was presented to Kenny by FE's Founder CEO Paul Ting at the 1 Million Quantum Pendant Celebration Banquet on 23rd May 2009.

Kenny is an inspiration to us all! To all FE Members and Leaders, if Kenny can do it, so can you! All you need is focus, commitment, determination, a great attitude and hard work, just like Kenny! Success only comes to those who work on it! AHOO! AHOO! AHOO!!!
